OL,3,CExcitement builds ahead of Jim Clark
OL,4,Crally in Scottish Borders
OL,6,FExcitement is building in the Scottish
OL,7,FBorders ahead of the Jim Clark rally
OL,8,Fwhich is a stage of the British Rally
OL,9,FChampionship.
OL,11,FThe rally is set to take place across
OL,12,Fthe weekend from Friday 23 May and
OL,13,Fmarks the halfway point of the British
OL,14,FRally Championship.
OL,16,FSpectators are hoping for local
OL,17,Fsuccess with local Duns driver Garry
OL,18,FPearson looking to make his mark
OL,19,Facross the weekend.
