OL,3,CExcitement builds ahead of Jim Clark
OL,4,Crally in Scottish Borders
OL,6,FThe rally in the Borders is one of the
OL,7,Flongest-running events on the British
OL,8,FRally Championship calendar, with
OL,9,Fclosed roads around Duns offering
OL,10,Ftechnical challenges for drivers on
OL,11,Fnarrow country roads.
OL,13,FIn a statement the British Rally
OL,14,FChampionship said: "Hailed as some of
OL,15,Fthe UK's most demanding asphalt
OL,16,Fstages, rallying legends and modern
OL,17,Fheroes have tackled the treacherous
OL,18,Flanes over the decades and in 2025,
OL,19,Fthe challenge is increased with around
OL,20,F100 competitive miles spread over two
OL,21,Fdays.
