OL,3,CExcitement builds ahead of Jim Clark
OL,4,Crally in Scottish Borders
OL,6,F"A mix of new tests and nostalgic
OL,7,Ffavourites that have defined the
OL,8,Frally's character are in store.
OL,10,F"The Jim Clark roads require respect,
OL,11,Fand hometown hero Garry Pearson knows
OL,12,Fhow to treat them. Having scored a
OL,13,Fpodium on the rally last year on
OL,14,Ffamiliar soil, he will be one to
OL,15,Fwatch, and along with co-driver Hannah
OL,16,FMcKillop, the pairing is fresh from a
OL,17,Fthird overall at Carlisle in their
OL,18,FFiesta Rally2."
