OL,3,CExcitement builds ahead of Jim Clark
OL,4,Crally in Scottish Borders
OL,6,FThe British Rally Championship says
OL,7,Fthe Borders roads usually provide a
OL,8,Flevel playing field for drivers and
OL,9,Fcall it a "demanding stage."
OL,11,FIn a statement they said: "An
OL,12,Fimpressive 100 stage miles lie ahead,
OL,13,Fincluding a brutal leg after dark on
OL,14,FFriday night.
OL,16,F"Demanding stages, narrow margins for
OL,17,Ferror, and the possibility of
OL,18,Fchangeable Scottish weather promise a
OL,19,Frollercoaster weekend that could
OL,20,Freshape the 2025 title hunt yet again."
